                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-44-defend440 t17991030-44-punish253"></join>
               whipped in the Jail
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. Justice BULLER.</p>
